          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Lines</text> and <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">CAD-Lines</text> also have <text styleclass="Popup Box2">XY-Axes</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small"> - </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" style="color:#ff0000;">but they are not displayed</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small"> in the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Graphic-area.</text> The <text styleclass="Popup Box2">X-axis</text> is from its <text styleclass="Popup Box2">start-Point</text> to its <text styleclass="Popup Box2">end-Point</text>. </para>
